overview: This annual gathering in Jamaica features all the best reggae musicians jamming at a positive-vibed event meant to promote peace, harmony and progressive Rasta teachings. Ranging in style from laid-back to energetic, edgy to inspirational, the performers include Cocoa Tea, Sanchez, Richie Stephens, Richie Spice, I Wayne, Admiral Tibett, Perfect, Warrior King, Gyptian, Jah Mason, L.U.S.T., Josie Mel, Kananga, Princess Ina and Zipper Ras.
title: Jam Jam: 2006: Part 1
